comment.commentLine: Note 1: for VM's UEK2 and UEK4 can not be mixed.
Dom0 needs to be equal or higher than DomU.
Note 2: As part of the deployment,
Oracle always installs the latest Exadata Storage software.
This means that different machines could have different versions of
the Storage software even if they are deployed around the same time.
An example of the difference between machines would be the Kernel
version that is installed. Please review the Exadata Storage
software version to be deployed with the Engineer during the
planning phase of the deployment.
Generic Questions:
Q1: For compute and storage nodes, will you want the current latest image?
If not, please indicate desired OS image.
Q2: For internal Cisco switch on the mgmt network (adm/ilom) STP is enabled by default,
Do you have BPDU Guard disabled on your uplink switch?
if not, we'll need to disable Spanning Tree Protocol on our side.
Compute Node Questions:
Q3: For 10G/25G Optical cables, do you have existing certified SFP Modules/Tranceivers?
Q4: For LACP, will you use default bond options?
If not, please specify desired bond options.
Q5: For DR machines,
have you ensured the RDBMS version matches the production/primary version?
Q6: For grid/oracle User Security with LDAP Servers,
have you confirmed the UID/GID's are matching your LDAP servers?
Expansion Questions:
Q7: Is this a fresh stand alone install?
If not, what other/existing engineered system will this machine
or these parts be connected to via Private (IB/RoCE) network.
Q8: Have you ensured that the Private (IB/RoCE) IPs do not overlap
and that they are in the proper subnet to match existing environment?
please confirm by checking /etc/hosts
Q9: Will the default client VIP suffice for SQL communication?
if not, a private VIP over the (IB/RoCE) fabric can be created,
please specify private vip hostnames and ips.
Q10: Have you ensured that the private IB/RoCE subnet does not overlap the
client, mgmt, and backup networks?
Q11: For storage expansion, do you want only new ASM diskgroups created?
Q12: For PXE imaging, we will bring an isolated switch, can you please provide
ethernet cable?
Additional Comments:
